OL,3,CBBC apologises after racial slur is
OL,4,Cbroadcast during Bafta ceremony
OL,6,FThe BBC has apologised for "any
OL,7,Foffence caused" after a racial slur
OL,8,Fshouted during the Bafta Film Awards
OL,9,Fceremony was broadcast on Sunday night.
OL,11,FThe slur was reportedly shouted by a
OL,12,Fmember of the audience who had
OL,13,FTourette syndrome as Sinners actors
OL,14,FDelroy Lindo and Michael B Jordan
OL,15,Fpresented the award for special visual
OL,16,Feffects at London's Royal Festival
OL,17,FHall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
