OL,3,CBBC apologises after racial slur is
OL,4,Cbroadcast during Bafta ceremony
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDuring the broadcast, the award
OL,12,Fceremony's presenter Alan Cumming
OL,13,Fissued an apology for the language
OL,14,Fviewers may hear.
OL,16,FHe said: "You may have heard some
OL,17,Fstrong and offensive language tonight.
OL,18,FIf you have seen the film I Swear, you
OL,19,Fwill know that film is about the
OL,20,Fexperience of a person with Tourette
OL,21,Fsyndrome.
OL,26,@xD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
