OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771916638
OL,3,CBBC apologises after racial slur is
OL,4,Cbroadcast during Bafta ceremony
OL,6,FAhead of the ceremony he had suggested
OL,7,Fthe awards show could trigger his tics.
OL,9,F"Certain things - like today, lots of
OL,10,Fpeople around, I'm feeling very, you
OL,11,Fknow, more tics in case I lash out.
OL,12,FDifferent situations can trigger
OL,13,Fdifferent emotions and tics and
OL,14,Fstuff," Mr Davidson told ITV News' US
OL,15,Fpartner CNN on the red carpet.
OL,17,FLeader of the Conservative Party Kemi
OL,18,FBadenoch described the BBC decision
OL,19,Fnot to cut the racial slur from the
OL,20,Ffinal programme as a "horrible
OL,21,Fmistake".
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
