SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771916638
OL,3,CBBC apologises after racial slur is
OL,4,Cbroadcast during Bafta ceremony
OL,6,F"Someone with Tourettes said something
OL,7,Fthey shouldn't have done, we are not
OL,8,Fgoing to blame their disability but it
OL,9,Fshould have been bleeped... That is a
OL,10,Fhuge error, that is the first thing
OL,11,Fthat the apology should've been made
OL,12,Ffor," she said on Good Morning Britain
OL,13,Fon Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
