OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1771916638
OL,3,CBBC apologises after racial slur is
OL,4,Cbroadcast during Bafta ceremony
OL,6,F"So, if it's being pre-recorded now,
OL,7,Fthen bleeping it out, for example,
OL,8,Fmight be a reasonable compromise. But
OL,9,FI think it has to be taken on a case-
OL,10,Fby-case kind of decision and scenario."
OL,12,FRobert Aramayo went on to win best
OL,13,Factor and the EE Rising Star award for
OL,14,Fplaying Mr Davidson in the film.
